{"tid":1589114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇學生巴絲發夢發到冇錢，想教小學功課輔班賺少少零用","createTime":"2019-09-23T06:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T06:53:54.000Z","uid":198801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"045346fe5fff8d54c1b18b64eba8735b91f02b53","tid":1589114,"uid":198801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"小弟幾年前大學畢業開左間屋邨補習社，<br />\n如果有中學大學巴絲發夢發到冇錢，<br />\n或者藍絲屋企人唔比零用，<br />\n但又唔想問其他人足借錢，<br />\n歡迎放學後黎我間補習社幫下手，自力更新賺少少零用<br />\n地點：觀塘區<br />\n人工：60-70/hr,  成本所限幫唔到太多，可以請到兩三位手足<br />\n時間：星期一至五 4:00-7:00左右，唔一定番足5日<br />\n有意留TG，唔洗話我知你點發夢，保障自己保障他人"},{"pid":"6efff6dcd6d9642fee92d2b8040981b05365ad00","tid":1589114,"uid":325882,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79a5447979b80670420c925936658518791d1f87","tid":1589114,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"54cb8cc45bbbfaa2ad3f70f1113e8826dbf63eef","tid":1589114,"uid":142004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/KkmmLllggf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKkmmLllggf&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK61tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=e7c2cd9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/KkmmLllggf</a>"},{"pid":"c94792ee8cea3c1cf50486b636b48cb6fae2dfa5","tid":1589114,"uid":198801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}